# Chinese Localization Guidelines for Game Studios (2026 Edition)

Maintained by ChineseGameLoc — https://chinesegameloc.com  
Technical guidelines for accurate, consistent, culturally aligned Simplified Chinese localization for video games.

This repository includes:
- Terminology rules
- UI and text constraints
- Cultural risk categories
- LQA workflow
- Platform-specific requirements (Bilibili, TapTap, Heybox, Xiaohongshu)

Designed for studios seeking reliable, process-driven Chinese localization across development, launch, and live-ops.

## About ChineseGameLoc
ChineseGameLoc provides boutique Chinese localization, LQA, and platform-native social media support for game studios.
